flowchart TD
    subgraph MH01["MH-01: Calendar User Flow"]
        U1[User opens Telegram Bot] --> U2[Clicks Calendar button]
        U2 --> U3[WebApp loads calendar view]
        U3 --> U4{Filter applied?}
        U4 -->|No| U5[Show all upcoming practices]
        U4 -->|Yes| U6[Show filtered practices]
        U5 --> U7[User selects practice]
        U6 --> U7
        U7 --> U8[Practice detail modal opens]
        U8 --> U9{User action?}
        U9 -->|Book| U10[Quick Booking MH-07]
        U9 -->|Back| U3
        U9 -->|Share| U11[Generate shareable link]
    end
